terms.definition: Tanner Scale Girl standardized character result for TANN0101-Stage 1: Pre-adolescent; elevation of papilla only.
terms.preferredTerm: Tanner Scale Girl TANN0101 Standardized Character Result Stage 1

terms.definition: Tanner Scale Girl standardized character result for TANN0101-Stage 2: Breast bud stage; elevation of breast and papilla as a small mound, enlargement of areola diameter.
terms.preferredTerm: Tanner Scale Girl TANN0101 Standardized Character Result Stage 2

terms.definition: Tanner Scale Girl standardized character result for TANN0101-Stage 3: Further enlargement of breast and areola, with no separation of their contours.
terms.preferredTerm: Tanner Scale Girl TANN0101 Standardized Character Result Stage 3

terms.definition: Tanner Scale Girl standardized character result for TANN0101-Stage 4: Projection of areola and papilla to form a secondary mound above the level of the breast.
terms.preferredTerm: Tanner Scale Girl TANN0101 Standardized Character Result Stage 4

terms.definition: Tanner Scale Girl standardized character result for TANN0101-Stage 5: Mature stage; projection of papilla only, due to recession of the areola to the general contour of the breast.
terms.preferredTerm: Tanner Scale Girl TANN0101 Standardized Character Result Stage 5
